ActJudges Act (Removal Allowance) Order
SubjectBRYK, The Hon. Donald P., RELOCATION EXPENSES
PrecisOrder prescribing additional periods during which certain RELOCATION EXPENSES may be reimbursed to The Hon. DONALD P. BRYK who was required to relocate to the City of Winnipeg in the Province of Manitoba, following his appointment as a Judge of Her Majesty’s Court of Queen’s Bench of Manitoba, on June 18, 2008.
